<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Details</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="StyleSheet2.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="product-details">
            <div class="image-section">
                <img src="batman-keychain.jpg" alt="Batman Key Chain">
            </div>
            <div class="info-section">
                <h2>Batman Key Chain</h2>
                <p class="price">$30</p>
                <span class="status">Available</span>
                <p class="description">
                    Another one of my best-selling keyrings is the Batman keyring. Over 50 of them are scattered all over Bangladesh right now.
                    The price and the details won't disappoint you. Buy this for someone who thinks they are Batman!
                </p>
                <p class="note"><strong>NOTE:</strong> Each item is made with the highest attention to quality and care; however, due to the nature of handmade items, gentle use is recommended.</p>
                <div class="quantity">
                    <label for="quantity">Quantity:</label>
                    <button class="decrease">-</button>
                    <input type="number" id="quantity" value="1" min="1">
                    <button class="increase">+</button>
                </div>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <button class="add-to-cart">Add to Cart</button>
                    <button class="buy-now">Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="related-products">
            <h3>You might also like</h3>
            <div class="product-list">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="captain-america-keychain.jpg" alt="Captain America Key Chain">
                    <p>Captain America Key Chain</p>
                    <p class="price">$30</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="duckling-keychain.jpg" alt="Duckling Key Chain">
                    <p>Duckling Key Chain</p>
                    <p class="price">$30</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="deadpool-keychain.jpg" alt="Deadpool Key Chain">
                    <p>Deadpool Key Chain</p>
                    <p class="price">$30</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
